data.name: Displayname_ViewStyle
data.value: ViewStyle

data.name: Description_ViewStyle
data.value: Controls how items are displayed in the control.

data.name: Displayname_ItemSize
data.value: ItemSize

data.name: Description_ItemSize
data.value: Sets the size of each RasterImageListItem in the control.

data.name: Displayname_ShowItemText
data.value: Enables item text.

data.name: Description_ShowItemText
data.value: Toggles whether the item text is shown in the control.

data.name: Displayname_Font
data.value: Font for item text.

data.name: Description_Font
data.value: Sets the font used to draw the item text.

data.name: Displayname_EnableKeyboard
data.value: Enables the keyboard.

data.name: Description_EnableKeyboard
data.value: Toggles whether the control automatically processes the keyboard.

data.name: Displayname_ScrollStyle
data.value: ScrollStyle

data.name: Description_ScrollStyle
data.value: Specifies the direction the RasterImageList Control scrolls the displayed items.

data.name: Displayname_SelectionMode
data.value: SelectionMode

data.name: Description_SelectionMode
data.value: Controls whether automatic item selection is allowed.

data.name: Displayname_Dock
data.value: Dock

data.name: Description_Dock
data.value: Determines which control borders are docked to its parent control and determines how a control is resized with its parent.

data.name: Displayname_AutoScroll
data.value: Enables auto scrolling.

data.name: Description_AutoScroll
data.value: Toggles whether the control enables auto scrolling.

data.name: Displayname_DoubleBuffer
data.value: Enables double buffer painting.

data.name: Description_DoubleBuffer
data.value: Toggles whether the control enables double buffer painting, which eliminates flicker.

data.name: Displayname_SizeMode
data.value: SizeMode

data.name: Description_SizeMode
data.value: Determines how the control displays the image and the automatic adjustments of the display rectangles.

data.name: Displayname_ScaleFactor
data.value: ScaleFactor

data.name: Description_ScaleFactor
data.value: The zoom factor used to display the image.

data.name: Displayname_InteractiveMode
data.value: InteractiveMode

data.name: Description_InteractiveMode
data.value: Controls user interaction with the control's display.
